		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The functionality of the Adaptoid that is missing is OS drivers for rumble support.  The hardware can do it but there are no drivers to allow games to use it yet.  I am hoping I can find someone that will easily write them.
<br />
<br />Not sure if the Adaptoid works without custom drivers either, or just uses the built in HID system.  Mine should work on any system that supports USB devices (Linux!).

		

